                <h1>Understanding the Impact of a White Background</h1>
                <p>A white background is often associated with clarity, simplicity, and purity. It provides a clean canvas that enhances the visibility of colors and elements, making designs feel more open and airy. This neutral backdrop fosters focus on the subject, allowing images or text to stand out, creating an inviting and modern aesthetic.</p>
